MTN has changed its prepaid data bundle portfolio. It made the adjustments based on an analysis of customer needs and market trends, said the company. The packages offer a wider selection, are tailored for a variety of customer usage and budget needs, and will be available from 5 March. “The new packages aim to offer more… are competitive within the market, and will reduce consumer worries of out-of-bundle bill surprises,” said MTN. The data bundles are listed below. MTN offers the following fortnightly data bundle: